{"tid":1909914,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【男女大不同之公投】D男仔究係淡左定係根本唔識？","createTime":"2020-03-04T09:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T16:21:28.000Z","uid":234788,"like":44,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a52b573c63ea31652c17bef9139bd2b622ff3a4","tid":1909914,"uid":234788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:48:56.000Z","msg":"呢排成日都見到唔同既絲打開POST講D男仔一拍拖就變得好冷淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔話女朋友冷落佢之類相對就少好多 (雖然唔係完全無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n其實究竟通常既情況係：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：男方其實都愛對方，係D女仔太容易無安全感，D男仔又get唔到對方想點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：男方無繼續好好愛對方，追到即高峰，唔識珍惜<br />\n<br />\n有無過來人分享下經驗同睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得：好多男仔唔珍惜，想珍惜既又唔識點先算係珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea3f01309ffdddd81f39c062a78f30946037432","tid":1909914,"uid":245499,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會係<br />\n女仔經常係咁記住個男仔最落力追佢嘅某幾次<br />\n條上限係咁向上搬 好似通脹咁<br />\n當上次係90分 今次就想要&gt;90分"},{"pid":"b1659857b0c9e885635ecfbc689c239602aa5461","tid":1909914,"uid":234788,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"cea3f01309ffdddd81f39c062a78f30946037432","tid":1909914,"uid":245499,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:20:18.000Z","msg":"會唔會係<br />\n女仔經常係咁記住個男仔最落力追佢嘅某幾次<br />\n條上限係咁向上搬 好似通脹咁<br />\n當上次係90分 今次就想要&gt;90分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T10:32:50.000Z","msg":"我都好想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma